## Cloning Process

1. **Read the analysis** - Understand structure, components, design tokens
2. **Determine format** - Check `--format` option or detect from project
3. **Set up theme** - Create theme file in format-appropriate style
4. **Build atoms first** - Buttons, inputs, text styles
5. **Build molecules** - Cards, form groups, nav items
6. **Build organisms** - Header, hero, feature sections
7. **Compose page** - Put sections together
8. **Add responsiveness** - Implement breakpoint behavior
9. **Add interactions** - Hover states, animations

